Sphere: Mind Sphere<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage cast sleep (target)<br/><br/>
<br/>
This spell will cause a humanoid target to fall asleep beyond normal<br/>
waking.  An attack or external influence will wake the target, but if the<br/>
spell is still effective, the target will soon fall asleep again.<br/>
